blic/pdf/wcp/ConciseGuide/EO_guide_full.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.labour.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fpublic%2Fpdf%2Fwcp%2FConciseGuide%2FEO_guide_full.pdf&d=%2BySIvleuZbSdMWEfOjMUQiL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=bfb48a99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/public/pdf/wcp/ConciseGuide/EO_guide_full.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n支票寫幾時無關係<br />\n總之你張支票 可以工資期屆滿後7天內兌現 就符合要求<br />\n<br />\n其實好多公司 尤其是現金流量比較緊張既<br />\n都好鍾意利用時間差去合法拖糧<br />\n<br />\n例如 <br />\n法例deadline係星期五 有D公司就會星期五下畫先叫你上去攞票 <br />\n合法拖你兩日糧"},{"pid":"d68ce0d0c6807978fab2cc4e2bef2a8af063e911","tid":1051103,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"40ee701ac6c18362140193e128a889a3cb4f4ae0","tid":1051103,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"660eda323074e0ae77e56eeab87d8cd3b54ffd2f","tid":1051103,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T10:35:24.000Z","msg":"今次係第一次7號都未出，之前拖吓都唔會過7號<br />\n<br />\n公司出支票，成日6 7號出票日期都寫上個月尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />究竟勞工署會唔會理呢啲細case"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T18:11:57.000Z","msg":"支付工資<br />\n工資在工資期最後一天完結時即到期支付，僱主必須盡快支付所有工資給僱員，在任何情況下不得遲於工資期屆滿後 7 天。僱主如果未能依時支付工資，須就欠薪支付利息給僱員<br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/public/pdf/wcp/ConciseGuide/EO_guide_full.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.labour.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fpublic%2Fpdf%2Fwcp%2FConciseGuide%2FEO_guide_full.pdf&d=%2BySIvleuZbSdMWEfOjMUQiL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=bfb48a99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/public/pdf/wcp/ConciseGuide/EO_guide_full.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n支票寫幾時無關係<br />\n總之你張支票 可以工資期屆滿後7天內兌現 就符合要求<br />\n<br />\n其實好多公司 尤其是現金流量比較緊張既<br />\n都好鍾意利用時間差去合法拖糧<br />\n<br />\n例如 <br />\n法例deadline係星期五 有D公司就會星期五下畫先叫你上去攞票 <br />\n合法拖你兩日糧"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T00:59:54.000Z","msg":"但係點證明到佢係例如8號出而唔係7號出"},{"pid":"ade7dae359fd37567ed8c9a689227d8cfc455ef0","tid":105